{"tid":2154981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突然諗起 香港投資咗咁撚多錢落\"亞投行\"","createTime":"2020-08-13T12:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T06:13:43.000Z","uid":57073,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"57a95c160f0ee600b6ce97ecadabdc31ebdd4fb7","tid":2154981,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"有無賺到$1 ???"},{"pid":"77aba0033505fcb2f96fbf8aad2a87a1e7f24709","tid":2154981,"uid":289708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:41:45.000Z","msg":"幫助國家係一種榮耀<br />\n唔應該計較賺蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe25d4389b660011cdf701d0936c095c1f9664a","tid":2154981,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:42:20.000Z","msg":"亞洲共榮圈"},{"pid":"dd9dd9e1242bfa742c0a3934821eee55d00d847e","tid":2154981,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e826d6075370c4fc7e7a7fd07bd3c92d49f89b07","tid":2154981,"uid":57073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"香港將捐款亞投行千萬美元　林鄭：在資金、人才方面作出貢獻<br />\n<br />\n2018年7月26 hk01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cff5242baddac9d5696172fc990dd93ee03e393","tid":2154981,"uid":116884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"借晒錢俾東南亞d公司 唔知有幾多間係假數呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c44afafc70ec6dc57f9eb4af9ea077e6b72ff98","tid":2154981,"uid":57073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"6月17日，亞洲基礎設施投資銀行（AIIB，下稱亞投行）批准了印度政府申請的7.5億美元（約合58億港元）貸款，以幫助該國抗擊新冠疫情。此貸款將用於支持印度防控和檢測新冠病毒，以及緩解新冠疫情對印度貧困弱勢家庭的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，這是印度為抗擊疫情向亞投行申請的第二筆貸款。今年5月，亞投行曾批准向印度提供5億美元的新冠肺炎應急貸款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975e4986179c52d6ad5bff312a4feac2148b456d","tid":2154981,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5cff5242baddac9d5696172fc990dd93ee03e393","tid":2154981,"uid":116884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"借晒錢俾東南亞d公司 唔知有幾多間係假數呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"嗰啲會唔會係支那去當地嘅「東南亞」公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2382471e05740b1f62c332effdd64e3e91fbd7","tid":2154981,"uid":299253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9d4688fe333bc77d0649e2e8d6c89249efb6d9","tid":2154981,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:47:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-06-20/424133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-06-20%2F424133&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=01fd3891\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-06-20/424133</a><br />\n<br />\n印度與中國爆發邊境衝突，造成20名印度士兵喪生，中方則被爆正副指揮官身亡。外電報導，在雙方15日衝突事件過後，由北京主導的亞洲基礎設施投資銀行（AIIB，簡稱亞投行），火速撥給印度政府7.5億美元的貸款，聲稱是要幫助印度對抗武漢肺炎疫情，但今年5月亞投行才撥了5億美元，不到1個月又貸款，被認為是變相「賠款」。<br />\n<br />\n印中關係緊張，亞投行卻在17日宣布，再撥款印度7.5億美元貸款，AIIB印度裔副總裁（投資業務部）兼首席投資官彭迪安（DJ Pandian）表示，AIIB對印度的支持，目的在防止武漢肺炎疫情長期損害印度經濟的生產能力，包括人力資本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該貸款項目由亞投行與亞洲開發銀行（ADB）共同出資22.50億美元，其中7.5億美元由亞投行提供，另外15億美元將由ADB提供。2016年1月開始運作的亞投行是一家多邊開發銀行，在全球已發展成為擁有102個成員的組織，目前由中國官員金立群擔任執行長，中國股份也占30%以上。<br />\n<br />\n令外界好奇的是，《大紀元時報》報導，亞投行曾在5月向印度提供5億美元的防疫應急貸款，當時印中士兵已經在邊境對峙，發生零星衝突，在15日造成印度士兵死亡後，中方又迅速在17日通過撥款，專家分析，極可能是中國希望拿錢息事寧人的「賠款」。"},{"pid":"26af912b67819babd3603cdaea111546d3dab07d","tid":2154981,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa422f728be52595039063af17d800f4c28bf0d","tid":2154981,"uid":116884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"975e4986179c52d6ad5bff312a4feac2148b456d","tid":2154981,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5cff5242baddac9d5696172fc990dd93ee03e393","tid":2154981,"uid":116884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"借晒錢俾東南亞d公司 唔知有幾多間係假數呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"嗰啲會唔會係支那去當地嘅「東南亞」公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:19:54.000Z","msg":"多數都係 或者中資扮新加坡資"},{"pid":"94dd6d9f0fe570ab1f3d69b0bb3e043fe9d36ad8","tid":2154981,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa422f728be52595039063af17d800f4c28bf0d","tid":2154981,"uid":116884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"975e4986179c52d6ad5bff312a4feac2148b456d","tid":2154981,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5cff5242baddac9d5696172fc990dd93ee03e393","tid":2154981,"uid":116884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"借晒錢俾東南亞d公司 唔知有幾多間係假數呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"嗰啲會唔會係支那去當地嘅「東南亞」公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T13:19:54.000Z","msg":"多數都係 或者中資扮新加坡資"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7194a7cc233adcc8f377479e647b46e9299b419","tid":2154981,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T06:13:43.000Z","msg":"???"}]}